§ 2689q. Repealed. Pub. L. 96–398, title VI, § 601(f), Oct. 7, 1980, 94 Stat. 1603
Section, Pub. L. 88–164, title II, § 231, as added Pub. L. 94–63, title III, § 303, July 29, 1975, 89 Stat. 328; amended Pub. L. 95–83, title III, § 308(g), Aug. 1, 1977, 91 Stat. 396; Pub. L. 95–622, title I, §§ 102(g), 108, Nov. 9, 1978, 92 Stat. 3412, 3417, set forth establishment, functions, etc., of the National Center for the Prevention and Control of Rape. See section 9511 et seq. of this title.
